Create Web applications for the E-commerce Industry.
● Create Model Product.
● Define a migration to create a products table with the necessary fields.
● Attributes: name, description, price, quantity, Product type
● Create Controller: ProductController with all method classes.
Create a new product record, display them in tabular format with an action button of delete and
edit. Also add a new field button on the right side corner to add a new record.
And on click of delete the record should be deleted and the record should be edited in different
pages.
Note: All fields are required fields. Product type should be in select option fields and price
should be decimal. Quantity should be only digits.
